    // Wipes every tile of `colorToClear` from the local grid. This is a
    // client-side prediction so a dead/disconnected player's territory
    // disappears instantly instead of waiting for many individual 'fa'
    // deltas to trickle in. Only call this from a confirmed elimination
    // event (pd/pr) — never from routine per-tile capture updates, since
    // the palette only has ~70 colors and collisions between concurrent
    // players are common. `force` skips the self/alive-player safety
    // checks below and should only be true when the local player is the
    // one who died.
